markets.rules_primary: If the highest temperature recorded in Central Park, New York for February 12, 2026 as reported by the National Weather Service's Climatological Report (Daily), is less than 32°, then the market resolves to Yes.

Preliminary NWS reporting and measurement methods may be subject to underlying rounding and conversion nuances. Traders should exercise caution when interpreting preliminary NWS data.
